description.en:
LOGS are needed to keep the fire (BONFIRESTELLAR) alive!
LOGS are apart of the Bonfirestellar Community. LOGS are used to compensate community Rep's and SR's for their hard work and commitment to the community. 
LOGS  is issued on a decentralized and open source blockchain platform. With over 10 thousand assets issued on the stellar network, its ideal to keep transaction speeds low and fast. No wonder Bonfirestellar is the communities token. For more information visit https://bonfirestellar.org/
